Procedure to build and run the game:

1.Open up a terminal and go to the current directory
2.Run the following command

>make clean

>make

>java Asteroids

The game will start!


Keyboard buttons:
1)ESC - Pauses the game
2)Enter - choose
3)E - Exits from the game

Player1:
1)UP/DOWN - thrust and back
2)LEFT/RIGHT - rotate direction
3)Alt - Shoots bullets from the spaceship

Player2:
1)W/A - thrust and back
2)S/D - - rotate direction
3)SPACE - Shoots bullets from the spaceship

